==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Lecanomancy
<hw>Le*can"o*man`cy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Gr.
<grk>leka`nh</grk> bowl or basin + <ets>-mancy</ets>.]</ety>
<def>Divination practiced with water in a basin, by throwing three
stones into it, and invoking the demon whose aid was sought.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Lecanoric</ent>⟦br⟧
